---
By: Annamalai Swami
Locus:
  Page: 454
  Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
Suffering gives us the impetus toescape from our self-limiting igno-rance.
If God did not send these gifts ofsuffering and misery, many peoplewould be
content to live their wholelives alienated from God and ignorantof their
true nature.
